  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566580/extras/5beff06ad5f94383f6fd770300ee377b.poster.avif?t=1765964683\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566580/extras/5beff06ad5f94383f6fd770300ee377b.webm?t=1765964683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566580/extras/5beff06ad5f94383f6fd770300ee377b.mp4?t=1765964683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Neocense is a 2D isometric puzzle game made in Unity. Explore the world of Cha as Amori, who has just discovered she has a rare gift called the Cense; she can connect with spirits and enter the realm of passing. <br>Through seeking the truth about her identity, Amori delves deeper into Chas past, The Hunters Army, and the history they've tried to bury. It's only a matter of time before she realizes the hardest unturned stones are the ones weighted with grief, and it's these which reveal the most about us.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Complete Puzzles</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566580/extras/3f7ce2a48f015707e3f5e06e8c895177.poster.avif?t=1765964683\" width=600 height=88 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566580/extras/3f7ce2a48f015707e3f5e06e8c895177.webm?t=1765964683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566580/extras/3f7ce2a48f015707e3f5e06e8c895177.mp4?t=1765964683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Preform Spirit Rituals</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/